57
00:04:08,916 --> 00:04:12,252
"If you want your necklace back,
give back the money"?

58
00:04:12,336 --> 00:04:14,546
"Will wait at the three cedars on
the mountain behind."

59
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,256
Signed, the Akagi Family.

60
00:04:17,216 --> 00:04:18,258
Money?

61
